"*Operational* or *Locked* state."
msgstr ""
"NetHSM s konfiguráciou. Stav *Provisioned* znamená buď stav *Operational*"
" alebo *Locked*."

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid "*Operational*"
msgstr "*Prevádzkové*"

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid ""
"NetHSM with configuration and ready to execute commands. The "
"*Operational* state implies the *Provisioned* state."
msgstr ""
"NetHSM s konfiguráciou a pripravený na vykonávanie príkazov. Stav "
"*Operational* znamená stav *Provisioned*."

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid "*Locked*"
msgstr "*Zamknuté*"

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid ""
