"<https://nethsmdemo.nitrokey.com/api_docs/nethsm-api.yaml>`_, pričom ju "
"možno skontrolovať a otestovať v prehliadači API ` "
"<https://nethsmdemo.nitrokey.com/api_docs/index.html>`_ ."

